title: Status message that gives information about each client connected to IQFeed and is received once per second after being turned on. See Admin Port System Messages

ClientID.title: Numeric identifier (unique by client type) for each client.

ClientName.title: Name of the client. This is set by the 3rd party app using the S,SET CLIENT NAME command on the socket connection it is connected to.

StartTime.title: Time the client connected to IQFeed.

Symbols.title: Number of symbols being watched by client. Only valid for Level 1 and Level 2 client types.

RegionalSymbols.title: Number of regional symbols being watched by client. Only valid for Level 1 client type.

KiloBytesReceived.title: Number of kilobytes received from the client.

KiloBytesSent.title: Number of kilobytes sent to the client.

KiloBytesQueued.title: Number of kilobytes queued by IQConnect waiting to be delivered to the client.
